create view PercentPopulationVaccinated as SELECT dea.continent, dea.location, dea.date, dea.population, vac.new_vaccinations, SUM(cast(vac.new_vaccinations as int)) OVER (partition by dea.location order by dea.location, dea.date) as RollingPeopleVaccinated FROM `capstone-project1997.portfolio_project.Covid_deaths` as dea join `capstone-project1997.portfolio_project.Covid_vaccinations` as vac on dea.location = vac.location and dea.date = vac.date where dea.continent is not null order by 2,3 create view PercentPopulationVaccinated as SELECT dea.continent, dea.location, dea.date, dea.population, vac.new_vaccinations, SUM(cast(vac.new_vaccinations as int)) OVER (partition by dea.location order by dea.location, dea.date) as RollingPeopleVaccinated FROM `capstone-project1997.portfolio_project.Covid_deaths` as dea join `capstone-project1997.portfolio_project.Covid_vaccinations` as vac on dea.location = vac.location and dea.date = vac.date where dea.continent is not null order by 2,3
